      </div>
      <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
        <l n="1'">I am Lipit-Ištar, the son of Enlil;</l>
        <l n="2'">in my palace of kingship, the pure and sweet dwelling,</l>
        <l n="3'">my spouse, holy Inanna,</l>
        <l n="1">established the foundation of my throne for me,</l>
        <l n="2">and therefore (will) embrace (me) until distant (time) and far-off days;</l>
        <l n="3">for the lady, I will spend the day with her in the sweet bedroom, the place where the heart is to rejoice;</l>
        <l n="4">I am Lipit-Ištar, the mighty heir,</l>
      </div>
